  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, guys, Essie here for Toys Unlimited.",
    "start": 42.943,
    "duration": 2.673
  },
  {
    "text": "And today, we are going to have fun",
    "start": 45.616,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "with Peppa Pig, her family,\nand some of her friends.",
    "start": 47.636,
    "duration": 3.868
  },
  {
    "text": "We are going to start with Suzy Sheep.",
    "start": 51.797,
    "duration": 2.782
  },
  {
    "text": "(bleats)",
    "start": 55.184,
    "duration": 1.274
  },
  {
    "text": "Here we have white play-doh.",
    "start": 56.458,
    "duration": 2.631
  },
  {
    "text": "White.",
    "start": 61.787,
    "duration": 1.073
  },
  {
    "text": "Suzy, would you like to have some toasts?",
    "start": 63.419,
    "duration": 2.479
  },
  {
    "text": "(bleats) That would be great.",
    "start": 66.471,
    "duration": 2.429
  },
  {
    "text": "(Essie) Here we have our toaster.",
    "start": 69.192,
    "duration": 2.289
  },
  {
    "text": "All we have to do is put\nour play-doh in there.",
    "start": 71.72,
    "duration": 3.683
  },
  {
    "text": "Just like that.",
    "start": 77.253,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "And we push it in.",
    "start": 79.364,
    "duration": 2.158
  },
  {
    "text": "Toasts are ready.",
    "start": 88.063,
    "duration": 1.482
  },
  {
    "text": "Yay, the toaster works great.",
