    "text": "(snorts)",
    "start": 148.812,
    "duration": 1.963
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, well, well, I would like\nto have a purple submarine. (snorts)",
    "start": 150.775,
    "duration": 4.531
  },
  {
    "text": "(Essie) Aye-aye, Captain Grandpa Pig.",
    "start": 155.768,
    "duration": 2.052
  },
  {
    "text": "Here is our purple play-doh.",
    "start": 158.132,
    "duration": 2.35
  },
  {
    "text": "Purple.",
    "start": 163.214,
    "duration": 1.462
  },
  {
    "text": "Submarine coming right up.",
    "start": 169.966,
    "duration": 2.698
  },
  {
    "text": "Here you go, Grandpa Pig.",
    "start": 184.907,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "Your very own purple submarine.",
    "start": 186.709,
    "duration": 2.55
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you. (snorts)",
    "start": 189.668,
    "duration": 1.714
  },
  {
    "text": "(Essie) Up next, we have Grandma Pig.",
    "start": 193.892,
    "duration": 2.621
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh-oh. Looks like Grandma Pig\nhas been playing in the muddy puddles.",
    "start": 196.793,
    "duration": 4.487
  },
  {
    "text": "She has mud splatters all over her.",
    "start": 201.663,
    "duration": 3.528
