  {
    "text": "(snorts) That's right.\nI love muddy puddles.",
    "start": 205.781,
    "duration": 2.711
  },
  {
    "text": "But now, I'm hungry.",
    "start": 208.492,
    "duration": 2.161
  },
  {
    "text": "How about some scoops of orange ice cream?",
    "start": 210.813,
    "duration": 3.88
  },
  {
    "text": "(Essie) To make an ice cream,",
    "start": 215.254,
    "duration": 1.291
  },
  {
    "text": "let's go ahead and put our play-doh\ninside our container.",
    "start": 216.545,
    "duration": 3.418
  },
  {
    "text": "Here is our ice cream cup.",
    "start": 220.186,
    "duration": 1.687
  },
  {
    "text": "And let's get our scooper.",
    "start": 222.053,
    "duration": 1.603
  },
  {
    "text": "First scoop of ice cream.",
    "start": 228.861,
    "duration": 1.396
  },
  {
    "text": "Second scoop.",
    "start": 234.947,
    "duration": 1.018
  },
  {
    "text": "Third one.",
    "start": 243.184,
    "duration": 1.173
  },
  {
    "text": "I think we can do one more.",
    "start": 244.852,
    "duration": 2.282
  },
  {
    "text": "And four.",
    "start": 253.551,
    "duration": 1.154
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, how about some sprinkles.",
    "start": 255.003,
    "duration": 1.952
  },
  {
    "text": "A little bit more.",
    "start": 259.104,
    "duration": 1.681
  },
  {
    "text": "And of course, our spoon.",
    "start": 262.623,
    "duration": 1.815
  },
  {
    "text": "(snorts) Oh, dear.\nIt sure looks delicious.",
    "start": 265.596,
    "duration": 3.202
  },
  {
    "text": "(Essie) Let's give it a try, Grandma Pig.",
