    "duration": 1.059
  },
  {
    "text": "And it is Daddy Pig's play-doh.",
    "start": 360.268,
    "duration": 2.401
  },
  {
    "text": "Daddy Pig is wearing a red dress.",
    "start": 363.368,
    "duration": 2.669
  },
  {
    "text": "And he also has a camera.",
    "start": 366.708,
    "duration": 2.142
  },
  {
    "text": "Say cheese.",
    "start": 369.845,
    "duration": 1.372
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, Daddy Pig, I think I want\nto make you some green beans.",
    "start": 373.246,
    "duration": 4.681
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's what we're going to need.",
    "start": 378.451,
    "duration": 1.53
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's put that right here.",
    "start": 382.322,
    "duration": 3.737
  },
  {
    "text": "Put our play-doh in the extruder.",
    "start": 386.364,
    "duration": 2.519
  },
  {
    "text": "And then we push it in.",
    "start": 390.302,
    "duration": 1.512
  },
  {
    "text": "There's our green beans.",
    "start": 395.584,
    "duration": 1.531
  },
  {
    "text": "We don't need that.",
    "start": 402.036,
    "duration": 1.381
  },
  {
    "text": "Green beans on a green plate.",
    "start": 413.006,
    "duration": 1.582
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah! It's George Pig's turn.",
    "start": 415.438,
    "duration": 2.467
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh-oh, George Pig has also been playing\nin the muddy puddles.",
    "start": 418.128,
    "duration": 4.851
  },
  {
    "text": "(snorts) Muddy puddles!",
    "start": 423.57,
    "duration": 2.914
  },
  {
    "text": "(Essie) Yup, that's right.",
    "start": 427.068,
    "duration": 1.289
  },
  {
    "text": "He has mud splatters all over him.",
    "start": 428.357,
    "duration": 2.911
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, George, here is your play-doh.",
    "start": 431.541,
    "duration": 2.456
  },
  {
    "text": "Color blue.",
    "start": 433.997,
    "duration": 1.412
  },
  {
    "text": "Blue.",
    "start": 439.346,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "What would you like me to make?",
    "start": 440.919,
    "duration": 1.851
  },
  {
    "text": "I want a dinosaur. Roar.",
    "start": 442.77,
    "duration": 3.778
  },
  {
    "text": "(Essie) We can definitely do that.",
    "start": 446.911,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's just roll up the play-doh first.",
    "start": 450.256,
    "duration": 2.54
  },
  {
    "text": "(roars)",
    "start": 461.248,
    "duration": 1.751
  },
  {
    "text": "Here is our dinosaur.",
    "start": 463.848,
    "duration": 1.982
  },
  {
    "text": "(roars)",
    "start": 476.016,
    "duration": 1.434
  },
  {
    "text": "Ooh, dinosaur.",
    "start": 477.933,
    "duration": 2.119
  },
  {
    "text": "Roar.",
    "start": 480.052,
    "duration": 1.25
  },
  {
    "text": "(roars)",
    "start": 481.553,
    "duration": 1.629
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi, I'm Peppa Pig,\nand I have red play-doh.",
    "start": 485.662,
    "duration": 3.946
  },
  {
    "text": "(Essie) Red play-doh.",
    "start": 489.867,
    "duration": 1.202
  },
  {
    "text": "Red.",
    "start": 494.518,
    "duration": 1.031
  },
  {
    "text": "And I would like to have\nsome red gumballs.",
    "start": 496.371,
    "duration": 3.23
  },
  {
    "text": "(Essie) To make our gumballs,\nwe are going to need...",
    "start": 499.941,
    "duration": 3.019
