  {
    "text": "our gumball maker.",
    "start": 503.218,
    "duration": 2.163
  },
  {
    "text": "First up is to roll our play-doh.",
    "start": 507.331,
    "duration": 3.55
  },
  {
    "text": "And then, we put it inside our dome.",
    "start": 513.294,
    "duration": 2.931
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's make our gumballs.",
    "start": 517.204,
    "duration": 1.91
  },
  {
    "text": "Ha, there it is.",
    "start": 523.875,
    "duration": 1.97
  },
  {
    "text": "Red gumballs.",
    "start": 525.845,
    "duration": 1.409
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's make some more.",
    "start": 527.747,
    "duration": 1.33
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa.",
    "start": 530.786,
    "duration": 1.151
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoops.",
    "start": 536.086,
    "duration": 1.195
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, yay! Gumballs. (snorts)",
    "start": 561.514,
    "duration": 2.993
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, everybody,\nthat's the end of our video.",
    "start": 564.848,
    "duration": 2.577
  },
  {
    "text": "I will see you again in our next episode.",
    "start": 567.425,
    "duration": 2.491
  },
  {
    "text": "This is Essie for Toys Unlimited.",
    "start": 569.916,
    "duration": 1.889
  },
  {
